# Info

Invoked when rendering the left side of the F3 debug screen, allowing you to add custom debug lines.

# Available Methods

- `event.add(text)` - Add a line to the debug screen

# Example

```js
ClientEvents.leftDebugInfo(event => {
	event.add('Custom Info: Hello!')
	event.add(`Player Position: ${Math.floor(event.player.x)}, ${Math.floor(event.player.y)}, ${Math.floor(event.player.z)}`)
})
```
